first time we need to get mongo drivers in our $gopath package directory
use following cmds
go get "github.com/gorilla/mux"
go get "go.mongodb.org/mongo-driver/mongo@~1.0.0"
or
dep ensure -add "go.mongodb.org/mongo-driver/mongo@~1.0.0"
if in your machine not having proper packages then you need to install it first
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
1.connect to mongodb database 
2.Start mongodb server with cmd mongod
3.After starting mongodb server run main program file 
4.send request through postman 
